WEBVTT

00:00:04.360 --> 00:00:09.160
VTT has decades of experience of
working with major cellular network, –

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:13.440
device and component manufacturers.

00:00:13.520 --> 00:00:19.680
Enhancing the reliability and efficiency of
telecommunication systems are our top priorities.

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:25.960
Our offering includes 5G and
beyond networks, cybersecurity, –

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:32.200
connectivity solutions for autonomous and
IoT systems, and satellite communications.

00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:36.520
Network resource sufficiency
is one of our central themes.

00:00:36.560 --> 00:00:42.760
End-to-end optimisation of network
resources, improving the quality of services –

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:49.000
in different vertical use cases and enabling
secure and trusted communications –

00:00:49.040 --> 00:00:53.320
are our main research
and development targets.

00:00:53.360 --> 00:00:59.560
Our research methods include future
concept and technology development, –

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:05.800
analytical and simulation-based research
and the practical implementation –

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:10.120
of proof-of-concept and
pre-commercial prototypes.

00:01:10.160 --> 00:01:14.440
We carry out joint funded and
direct contract research –

00:01:14.480 --> 00:01:18.720
and development for our customers, –

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:23.000
and act also as a subcontractor
for industry in large R&D projects.

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:28.080
We have a unique test network platform
for proof-of-concept showcasing, –

00:01:28.120 --> 00:01:32.400
private network studies and
for supporting R&D projects.

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:36.720
Serving fields ranging from
defence and public safety –

00:01:36.760 --> 00:01:41.000
to maritime, traffic and arctic solutions, –

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:46.240
our industrial verticals offering
includes e.g. positioning solutions, –

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:52.480
AI/ML deployment for ICT processes, IoT
connectivity and industrial network solutions.

00:01:52.520 --> 00:01:58.760
Our cyber security portfolio includes security
solutions for communication networks, –

00:01:58.800 --> 00:02:03.920
industrial systems and devices and
services, along with applied cryptography, –

00:02:03.960 --> 00:02:08.280
AI and risk management solutions.

00:02:08.320 --> 00:02:12.360
Our services include testing for
vulnerabilities and performance –

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:16.960
and helping our customers to
build more robust solutions.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:21.120
Guiding you towards the smart
networks and services of the future, –

00:02:21.160 --> 00:02:25.120
we can help you with all your R&D,
testing,  qualification, –

00:02:25.160 --> 00:02:29.040
and IPR business needs.
